1
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:04,120
Son, let's do it again, okay?

2
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:04,560
Here.

3
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,480
Xiaoyong, pass the ball!

4
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,680
Pass it! Don't just stand there!

5
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,519
Xiaoyong!

6
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:18,959
Attack!

7
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,040
Don't freeze up!

8
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:36,840
Thank you.

9
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:37,840
Thank you.

10
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,040
First, I want to thank my father.

11
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,439
He's the one who protected

12
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,840
my love for football.

13
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,799
I also want to thank my mother.

14
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,640
She's the one

15
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,480
who worked so hard all these years

16
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,599
to raise me.

17
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:50,799
And Coach Chang.

18
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,079
Coach Chang,

19
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,959
for guiding and supporting me

20
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,079
throughout my football career,

21
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:56,959
always being there for me.

22
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,480
My girlfriend...

23
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,200
My girlfriend's father...

24
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,599
A grown man like him,

25
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,599
still without a job.

26
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,680
How's he ever going to

27
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,359
provide for your daughter?

28
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,439
Let me tell you,

29
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:06,760
I can support myself.

30
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,039
Is it your dad?

31
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:37,879
Does he disapprove of me?

32
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:43,759
Yaoyao,

33
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,199
I'm sorry. Please don't be upset.

34
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,120
How about this?

35
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,280
After I finish this Jiangsu Super League,

36
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:54,199
I'll focus on finding a real job.

37
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,400
I'll try to make your dad happy.

38
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,080
No need.

39
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,080
Do whatever you want to do.

40
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:02,639
As long as you're happy with it.

41
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,879
Think of it as me repaying Coach Chang.

42
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:05,639
Okay?

43
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,560
He's coached me since I was a kid.

44
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,280
I've always hoped

45
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,960
to do something for him.

46
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,840
You don't have to tell me all this.

47
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,400
If he's so good to you,

48
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,759
then go live your life with him.

49
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,159
You're what matters most.

50
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,520
In my life,

51
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,520
you are the most important person.

52
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,199
Please don't be sad.

53
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,120
If worse comes to worst,

54
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:31,479
I'll go tell the team

55
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,439
that I'm quitting.

56
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:39,120
I'm not telling you to stop playing.

57
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:40,520
I just feel like

58
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:42,280
you don't really care about me.

59
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,520
How could I not

60
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,439
care about you?

61
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:45,800
Then tell me,

62
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,120
what day is today?

63
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,319
Today is our

64
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,319
dating anniversary.

65
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,479
And you still made me angry?

66
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,719
I got this especially for you.

67
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,080
Alright then.

68
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:16,680
A job

69
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,959
can be found later.

70
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,519
Money can be earned later too.

71
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:21,439
But this tournament

72
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,279
is now or never.

73
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,279
I know doing this

74
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,279
seems kind of irresponsible.

75
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,879
Even if we win the Jiangsu Super League,

76
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,199
it won't bring us much.

77
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:36,639
But Yaoyao,

78
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,399
this is the last time in my life,

79
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,439
my last chance,

80
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,439
and my only chance,

81
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,800
to ever be this close to my dream.

82
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:49,959
I know.

83
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,519
Grand narratives,

84
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:37,600
tech advancements,

85
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,439
people's livelihoods...

86
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,439
Every topic

87
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,519
has already been covered.

88
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,399
Where's the fresh angle?

89
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,279
Where's the fresh angle?

90
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,319
Stop being so hard on yourself.

91
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,360
Have something warm to drink.

92
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,120
Here.

93
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,480
Let me show you something funny.

94
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:01,240
Look.

95
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,839
Netizens from all over the country

96
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,199
are renaming Changzhou.

97
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,439
What's this one?

98
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,720
Loser-zhou.

99
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,519
And this one?

100
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,560
Towel-zhou.

101
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,199
What's that?

102
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,439
Stick-zhou.

103
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,959
And by the end of it,

104
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,000
it's "Thirteenth Sister."

105
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,240
Honey,

106
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,759
you've got some thick skin.

107
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,199
On the surface,

108
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,720
they're just teasing Changzhou,

109
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,920
but really they're mocking

110
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:22,439
our Changzhou Team for being bad.

111
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,560
We've played for so long

112
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,920
and haven't scored a single goal.

113
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,240
Just losing and losing,

114
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,120
failing over and over.

115
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:28,519
So my speech draft,

116
00:06:28,519 --> 00:06:29,240
how should I title it?

117
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,920
"On How a Team

118
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,319
Keeps Failing"?

119
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,519
So what if they fail?

120
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,040
Honey,

121
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,399
the way I see it,

122
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,560
losing doesn't matter.

123
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,079
It's that spirit deep inside

124
00:06:41,279 --> 00:06:42,519
that's the most precious thing.

125
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,920
It's called Resilience.

126
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,040
In the past,

127
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,439
you always wanted to film

128
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,759
those glamorous things.

129
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,040
But have you ever thought,

130
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,639
that the truly great stories,

131
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,079
aren't they about people like you?

132
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,399
Falling down time after time,

133
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,800
saying "I'm fine,"

134
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,240
but getting up again and again,

135
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,600
just ordinary people

136
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,439
charging forward?

137
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,439
Honey, you're pretty good!

138
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,759
Of course.

139
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:06,319
I'm a Project 985 grad, after all.

140
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,120
What you brought isn't milk,

141
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,319
it's pure inspiration.

142
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,519
Then I deserve a reward! A reward!

143
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,920
I have an angle now. You get some rest.

144
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,040
Okay, okay.

145
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,759
We could never get an interview with him.

146
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:25,879
What he always says is,

147
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:27,040
"Go interview the players."

148
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,040
That's just how Old Chang is.

149
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,959
It's normal that you can't interview him.

150
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,480
Usually, at home,

151
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,839
he's quiet as a clam.

152
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:34,519
And this guy,

153
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,720
he really doesn't like showing off.

154
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,439
When he was young,

155
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,240
he was stubborn,

156
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,279
and never made it as a player.

157
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,720
Later he became a coach,

158
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,720
and focused

159
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,519
entirely

160
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,439
on these kids.

161
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,000
But this time he specifically chose

162
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,040
Xiaoyong as captain.

163
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:47,800
Why?

164
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,920
As for Xiaoyong,

165
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,360
he's sensible, hardworking,

166
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:54,000
and fights hard on the pitch.

167
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,879
When he got injured,

168
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:57,879
we all felt it was such a shame.

169
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,759
I remember the day Xiaoyong got hurt,

170
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:02,000
Chang Yi came home

171
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:03,240
and got himself completely drunk.

172
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,519
His heart really aches for Xiaoyong.

173
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:08,600
This time, making Xiaoyong captain,

174
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,959
I think Old Chang knows

175
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,000
Xiaoyong has a mental hurdle to overcome.

176
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,439
He wanted to throw him a rope

177
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,439
so he could climb out himself.

178
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,240
The reporter is here for an interview.

179
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,240
If you won't talk, I will.

180
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:29,399
This kid has been sharp since he was little.

181
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,879
Playing football every single day.

182
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:32,000
In this little alley here,

183
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,200
running around all over.

184
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,720
He even once won

185
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,000
the championship at the Provincial Games.

186
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,840
If he hadn't gotten injured back then,

187
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,759
by now, who knows,

188
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:40,240
he might be on the national team.

189
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,679
Enough about the national team.

190
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:44,000
You just mentioned he was injured.

191
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,360
What kind of injury was it?

192
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,399
Stop it, all of you.

193
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,159
Listen, Reporter,

194
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,519
the Changzhou Team right now

195
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:51,720
has been losing game after game.

196
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,600
My son,

197
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,200
he's under a lot of pressure.

198
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,360
Online,

199
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,000
so many people are bashing him.

200
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,480
I really hope all of you

201
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,000
will stop bothering him.

202
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,080
Let him play football in peace.

203
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,639
Ma'am,

204
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:04,159
please believe me.

205
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,320
I'm also a mother myself.

206
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,559
And I'm a firm supporter

207
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:08,399
of our Changzhou Team.

208
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:08,679
Yes.

209
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:09,759
Our visit today

210
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,000
is definitely not to reopen old wounds.

211
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,600
We hope that through

212
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:14,600
this interview,

213
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,279
more people

214
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,679
will get to know the real players,

215
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,039
and the real side of this team.

216
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,600
Xiaoyong's mom,

217
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,679
have a proper chat with the reporter.

218
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:23,919
Sit down and talk.

219
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:24,799
Ma'am, please sit.

220
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:28,559
Go on.

221
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,639
Tell me

222
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,600
the story behind all this.

223
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,519
His dad,

224
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,320
seeing that he loved football,

225
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,919
whenever he had free time,

226
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,320
he'd play with him.

227
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,360
Then later,

228
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,200
his dad developed heart problems.

229
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:44,120
The doctor said

230
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,120
he couldn't get too worked up.

231
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,600
So I

232
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,960
didn't let them play football,

233
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,799
or watch games either.

234
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,440
But the two of them,

235
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:55,600
they'd still sneak off to watch.

236
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:56,720
Goal!

237
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,240
Your mom's asleep.

238
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:01,919
Daddy,

239
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,519
one day I'll represent the Chinese team

240
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,840
and make it to the World Cup.

241
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,639
Son, I hope that

242
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,879
besides being happy,

243
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:11,919
you can become

244
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,159
the real man of this family.

245
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:15,519
Protect your mom.

246
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,840
Take good care of her.

247
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,799
Promise Daddy, okay?

248
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,720
That's my boy.

249
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:24,919
Later on,

250
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:26,799
his dad passed away.

251
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,879
Whenever he missed his dad,

252
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,039
he'd be all by himself,

253
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,960
secretly kicking a ball around.

254
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,320
It broke my heart to see him like that.

255
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,399
So I sent him to

256
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,679
train with Coach Chang.

257
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,440
Xiao Xie, you're too slow!

258
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,519
Pick up the pace, keep up!

259
00:10:50,639 --> 00:10:51,440
Don't slow down!

260
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,960
This path isn't an easy one.

261
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,559
If you want to succeed,

262
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:00,879
you have to put in

263
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:02,080
five times the effort of others,

264
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:03,879
even ten times more.

265
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,679
Who would've thought,

266
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:09,039
this training would turn out so well.

267
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,000
Originally,

268
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,679
this was a great thing.

269
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:13,960
But...

270
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,080
Xiaoyong,

271
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,120
got any plans after work?

272
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,080
How about

273
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,559
having a few drinks with Master?

274
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:23,519
Maybe another time, Master.

275
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,559
After work,

276
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,240
I need to buy groceries for my mom.

277
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,039
Alright, alright.

278
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,600
If I had a son like you,

279
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:31,639
that'd be wonderful.

280
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,840
Dinner time!

281
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,000
Master, I'm heading off.

282
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:38,799
Dinner's ready.

283
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,399
Get down!

284
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:48,960
Master!

285
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:05,440
Later on,

286
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:06,799
his lower leg

287
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,240
suffered a comminuted fracture.

288
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:11,200
His joints and ligaments were injured too.

289
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,200
Now,

290
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,159
so many people online

291
00:12:14,679 --> 00:12:15,200
are gossiping about

292
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,639
our kids.

293
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,039
Reporter,

294
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,879
you've got to write a good piece.

295
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,399
It's me.

296
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,480
My old life

297
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,919
dragged Xiaoyong down.

298
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:26,600
Xiaoyong

299
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,080
has always been

300
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,039
a great talent at football.

301
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,360
Ever since the accident,

302
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,039
he refuses to come to the worksite anymore.

303
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,799
It breaks my heart.

304
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,200
Today,

305
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,200
he's playing for Changzhou.

306
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,679
I've got to cheer him on

307
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,360
and support him.

308
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:46,279
Xiaoyong,

309
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,879
we watched him grow up.

310
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,159
He really is a good kid.

311
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:50,840
We've got to cheer

312
00:12:50,879 --> 00:12:51,759
and applaud for him.

313
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,159
That's right.

314
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,159
Thank you all.

315
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,480
Full support!

316
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,600
Thank you, thank you.

317
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:27,440
With this extra training,

318
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,440
I'm completely out of breath.

319
00:14:28,919 --> 00:14:30,279
Our stamina is just terrible.

320
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:31,759
No wonder we lost three in a row.

321
00:14:31,799 --> 00:14:32,320
Exactly.

322
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,879
Even our ball control has gotten worse.

323
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,000
We've gotta keep training.

324
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,360
The next few matches

325
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,039
are all gonna be tough fights.

326
00:14:39,559 --> 00:14:40,120
What are we gonna do?

327
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,000
Hey, guys,

328
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,639
I've got some good news for you.

329
00:14:47,759 --> 00:14:48,519
I had a dream.

330
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:50,320
I dreamed that

331
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,240
in our next match,

332
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:53,480
we scored a goal.

333
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,080
Don't laugh.

334
00:14:55,919 --> 00:14:57,639
Either you guys scored,

335
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,279
or I scored.

336
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,279
Anyway, somebody definitely scored.

337
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,440
Why didn't you

338
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,399
dream of scoring a few more?

339
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:06,360
How about this?

340
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,320
Let's bet two hundred bucks.

341
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:09,240
Deal.

342
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,559
If you score,

343
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,399
I'll give you two hundred.

344
00:15:11,759 --> 00:15:12,559
It's a deal.

345
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:13,679
Alright!

346
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,639
Pack up, let's go get some sleep.

347
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:17,639
Let's go.

348
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:18,639
Come on.

349
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,000
So good.

350
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,440
Help me carry the water.

351
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,000
Big Bro,

352
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,360
nobody wants these tickets anymore.

353
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,879
Brothers, listen up.

354
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,240
The players out on the field

355
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,759
are giving it their all.

356
00:15:36,879 --> 00:15:37,840
So off the field,

357
00:15:38,759 --> 00:15:40,120
we just have to put our pride on the line.

358
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:41,679
I don't care

359
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:42,600
what method you use.

360
00:15:43,279 --> 00:15:44,960
Relatives, friends, classmates, coworkers,

361
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,639
drag in anyone you can.

362
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:48,480
Even the pancake vendor on the street,

363
00:15:48,679 --> 00:15:49,600
drag them in too.

364
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:50,159
You hear me?

365
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,559
Big Bro, there's really no one left.

366
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:53,879
Yeah, there's really no one.

367
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:55,240
What's the problem?

368
00:15:56,399 --> 00:15:57,639
Are you going to let a minor bump stop you?

369
00:15:58,039 --> 00:15:59,120
I hate it when you talk like that.

370
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:00,879
Come on.

371
00:16:01,279 --> 00:16:01,840
If you can't find people,

372
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:02,759
go pull them off the streets.

373
00:16:02,759 --> 00:16:03,879
There are tons of people walking by.

374
00:16:04,399 --> 00:16:05,240
Just tell them,

375
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,840
"You're not just here to watch a game,

376
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,039
you're here to back up

377
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:08,679
the people of Changzhou."

378
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:10,639
Even if it's a dog,

379
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,759
drag it in if you can.

380
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:12,720
You hear me?

381
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:14,919
Did you hear me?

382
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,080
Okay, okay, okay.

383
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:16,879
Get going!

384
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,279
Play physical, hold your position!

385
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:05,880
Xiaoyong, catch!

386
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,880
Pass to Zhou Hang! To Zhou Hang!

387
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:24,279
That's a foul!

388
00:17:27,519 --> 00:17:28,279
It was so obvious!
